## 2) Workspaces

### `/app/workspaces`
- Load:
  - `GET /workspaces`
- Fields nên render:
  - `id`
  - `name`
  - `slug`
  - `status`
  - `role`
  - `joinedAt`
- Actions:
  - Switch:
    - `POST /workspaces/:workspaceId/switch`

### `/app/workspaces/new`
- Action:
  - `POST /workspaces`

### Body
```json
{
  "name": "Demo Workspace",
  "slug": "demo-workspace",
  "billing": {
    "billingType": "ORGANIZATION",
    "companyName": "Demo Company",
    "taxCode": "0312345678",
    "address": "123 Demo Street",
    "invoiceEmail": "billing@demo.com",
    "representativeName": "Nguyen Van A",
    "phone": "0901234567"
  }
}
```

### Individual body
```json
{
  "name": "Demo Workspace",
  "slug": "demo-workspace",
  "billing": {
    "billingType": "INDIVIDUAL",
    "fullName": "Nguyen Van B",
    "citizenId": "079123456789",
    "taxCode": "8561234567",
    "address": "123 Demo Street",
    "invoiceEmail": "demo.user@example.com",
    "phone": "0901234567"
  }
}
```

