## 3) Templates

### `/app/w/:workspaceId/templates`
- Load:
  - `GET /workspaces/:workspaceId/templates`
- Fields nên render:
  - `id`
  - `name`
  - `code`
  - `status`
  - `createdAt`
  - `updatedAt`

### `/app/w/:workspaceId/templates/new`
- Action:
  - `POST /workspaces/:workspaceId/templates`

### Create body
```json
{
  "name": "Template Demo",
  "content": "<zns>..</zns>",
  "placeholdersJson": { "name": "string" }
}
```

### `/app/w/:workspaceId/templates/:templateId`
- Load:
  - `GET /workspaces/:workspaceId/templates/:templateId`
- Actions:
  - Update:
    - `PATCH /workspaces/:workspaceId/templates/:templateId`
  - Submit:
    - `POST /workspaces/:workspaceId/templates/:templateId/submit`
  - Disable (Owner only):
    - `POST /workspaces/:workspaceId/templates/:templateId/disable`

---

## 4) Messaging

### `/app/w/:workspaceId/messages/send-single`
- Load gợi ý:
  - `GET /workspaces/:workspaceId/templates`
  - `GET /workspaces/:workspaceId/oa/status`
  - `GET /workspaces/:workspaceId/wallet/balance`
- Action:
  - `POST /workspaces/:workspaceId/messages/send-single`

### Body
```json
{
  "templateId": "TEMPLATE_ID",
  "phoneNumber": "84901234567",
  "data": { "name": "Minh" }
}
```

### `/app/w/:workspaceId/messages/logs`
- Load:
  - `GET /workspaces/:workspaceId/messages/logs?status=SUCCESS&sendType=SINGLE&limit=50`

---

