## 6) Members

### `/app/w/:workspaceId/members`
- Load:
  - `GET /workspaces/:workspaceId/members`
- Invite:
  - `POST /workspaces/:workspaceId/invitations`
- Accept invitation:
  - `POST /workspaces/:workspaceId/invitations/accept`
- Remove member:
  - `DELETE /workspaces/:workspaceId/members/:memberUserId`

### Invite body
```json
{
  "inviteType": "EMAIL",
  "inviteValue": "member@example.com",
  "role": "MEMBER"
}
```

### Accept body
```json
{
  "token": "INVITE_TOKEN"
}
```

