## 9) API Keys

### `/app/w/:workspaceId/api-keys`
- Load:
  - `GET /workspaces/:workspaceId/api-keys`
- Actions:
  - Create:
    - `POST /workspaces/:workspaceId/api-keys`
  - Disable:
    - `PATCH /workspaces/:workspaceId/api-keys/:apiKeyId/disable`
